<plot>Greek Light examines the lives of three old-school fishermen in the eccentric and trendy island hot-spot, Mykonos. We see the effects of modern tourism on the work of these fishermen. More than anything it is about the camaraderie of these soon-to-be vanished professionals in the face of a new, young, modern world.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?222590</url></doc>
